# Agent worktrees created by Claude Code when sub-agents need an isolated
# copy of the repository. Transient — not part of the project.
.claude/

# Cloudflare Wrangler local state and per-user config. The repo ships
# worker/wrangler.toml.example; each deployer creates their own
# worker/wrangler.toml with their KV namespace id (see worker/README.md).
.wrangler/
worker/.wrangler/
worker/wrangler.toml
